<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Comprobante de transacción SPEI</title>
    <style>
        /* poppins-latin-400-normal */
        @font-face {
            font-family: 'Poppins';
            font-style: normal;
            font-display: swap;
            font-weight: 400;
            src: url('https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/fontsource/fonts/poppins@latest/latin-400-normal.woff2') format('woff2'), url('https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/fontsource/fonts/poppins@latest/latin-400-normal.woff') format('woff');
            unicode-range: U+0 -00FF, U+131, U+152 -0153, U+2BB-02BC, U+2C6, U+2 DA, U+2 DC, U+304, U+308, U+329, U+2000 -206F, U+2074, U+20 AC, U+2122, U+2191, U+2193, U+2212, U+2215, U+FEFF, U+FFFD;
        }

        /* poppins-latin-500-normal */
        @font-face {
            font-family: 'Poppins';
            font-style: normal;
            font-display: swap;
            font-weight: 500;
            src: url('https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/fontsource/fonts/poppins@latest/latin-500-normal.woff2') format('woff2'), url('https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/fontsource/fonts/poppins@latest/latin-500-normal.woff') format('woff');
            unicode-range: U+0 -00FF, U+131, U+152 -0153, U+2BB-02BC, U+2C6, U+2 DA, U+2 DC, U+304, U+308, U+329, U+2000 -206F, U+2074, U+20 AC, U+2122, U+2191, U+2193, U+2212, U+2215, U+FEFF, U+FFFD;
        }

        /* poppins-latin-600-normal */
        @font-face {
            font-family: 'Poppins';
            font-style: normal;
            font-display: swap;
            font-weight: 600;
            src: url('https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/fontsource/fonts/poppins@latest/latin-600-normal.woff2') format('woff2'), url('https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/fontsource/fonts/poppins@latest/latin-600-normal.woff') format('woff');
            unicode-range: U+0 -00FF, U+131, U+152 -0153, U+2BB-02BC, U+2C6, U+2 DA, U+2 DC, U+304, U+308, U+329, U+2000 -206F, U+2074, U+20 AC, U+2122, U+2191, U+2193, U+2212, U+2215, U+FEFF, U+FFFD;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            position: relative;
            height: 100dvh;
        }

        .background-image {
            position: absolute;
            width: 50%;
            top: 50%;
            left: -25%;
            filter: blur(8px);
            -webkit-filter: blur(8px);
            z-index: -1;
        }

        .container {
            width: 100%;
            height: 100dvh;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin: 0 0 10px;
        }

        h2 {
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: 500;
            color: white;
            margin: 20px 0 10px;
        }

        hr.solid {
            border-top: 2px solid #000;
            margin: 10px 0;
        }

        .company-info {
            font-size: 12px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #221F20;
            text-wrap: balance;
        }

        .details-table {
            width: 100%;
            font-size: 14px;
        }

        .details-table tr td {
            padding: 8px 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #D0D0D0;
        }

        .details-table tr:last-child td {
            border-bottom: 0;
        }

        .details-table tr td.separator {
            padding: 0 8px;
            /* Ajuste de padding para la línea vertical */
            border-bottom: 0;
        }

        .subtitle {
            color: #03194D;
            font-weight: bold;
            width: 30%;
        }

        .value {
            width: 70%;
            color: #004FE7;
        }

        .note {
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #878787;
        }

        img {
            max-width: 100%;
            height: auto;
        }

        .title {
            background-color: #001750;
            vertical-align: center;
            padding-bottom: 1px;
            padding-top: 1px;
            padding-inline: 8px;
            border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0;
        }

    </style>
</head>

<body>
<div class="container">
    <header>

        <h1>Comprobante de Transacción SPEI</h1>
        <hr class="solid">
        <div style="margin-bottom:36px;margin-top:36px">
            <img class="cpay-logo" src="https://viabo.com/production_images/cpay/cpay-logo.png" alt="logo central pay">
            <h6 style="color:#878787;margin:0px">Top System SAPI de CV</h6>
            <p class="company-info">Fuente del rey #95 Lomas de Tecamachalco C.P. 52780 Naucalpan Edo. de México, México
            </p>
        </div>
    </header>


    <div>
        <div class="title">
            <h2>
                <img alt="cpay-money-icon" src="https://viabo.com/production_images/cpay/cpay-icon-money.png"
                     style="width: 25px; height: 25px; vertical-align: middle;margin-right:8px">
                Resumen Transacción
            </h2>
        </div>

        <table class="details-table">
            <tr>
                <td class="subtitle">Monto:</td>
                <td class="separator"></td>

                <td class="value">
                    <b>{{ amount }}</b>
                </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td class="subtitle">Tipo:</td>
                <td class="separator"></td>
                <td class="value">
                    <b>{{ transactionType }}</b>
                </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td class="subtitle">Concepto:</td>
                <td class="separator"></td>
                <td class="value">
                    <b>{{ concept }}</b>
                </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td class="subtitle">Fecha:</td>
                <td class="separator"></td>
                <td class="value">
                    <b>{{ date }}</b>
                </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td class="subtitle">Estatus:</td>
                <td class="separator"></td>
                <td class="value">
                    <b>{{ statusName }}</b>
                </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td class="subtitle">Clave de Rastreo:</td>
                <td class="separator"></td>
                <td class="value">
                    <b>{{ reference }}</b>
                </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td class="subtitle">Validar Transferencia:</td>
                <td class="separator"></td>
                <td class="value">
                    <a href="https://www.banxico.org.mx/cep/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
                        <b>https:/www.banxico.org.mx/cep/</b>
                    </a>
                </td>
            </tr>
        </table>
    </div>


    <div>
        <div class="title">
            <h2>
                <img alt="cpay-icon=wallet" src="https://viabo.com/production_images/cpay/cpay-icon-wallet.png"
                     style="width: 25px; height: 25px; vertical-align: middle;margin-right:8px">
                Ordenante
            </h2>
        </div>
        <table class="details-table">
            <tr>
                <td class="subtitle">Nombre:</td>
                <td class="separator"></td>
                <td class="value">
                    <b>{{ sourceName }}</b>
                </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td class="subtitle">CLABE:</td>
                <td class="separator"></td>
                <td class="value">
                    <b>{{ sourceAccount }}</b>
                </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td class="subtitle">Medio de Pago:</td>
                <td class="separator"></td>
                <td class="value">
                    <b>SPEI</b>
                </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td class="subtitle">Institución:</td>
                <td class="separator"></td>
                <td class="value">
                    <b>STP</b>
                </td>
            </tr>
        </table>
    </div>

    <div>
        <div class="title">
            <h2>
                <img alt="cpay-icon=wallet" src="https://viabo.com/production_images/cpay/cpay-icon-wallet.png"
                     style="width: 25px; height: 25px; vertical-align: middle;margin-right:8px">
                Beneficiario
            </h2>
        </div>
        <table class="details-table">
            <tr>
                <td class="subtitle">Nombre:</td>
                <td class="separator"></td>
                <td class="value">
                    <b>{{ destinationName }}</b>
                </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td class="subtitle">RFC:</td>
                <td class="separator"></td>
                <td class="value">
                    <b>{{ destinationRfc }}</b>
                </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td class="subtitle">CLABE:</td>
                <td class="separator"></td>
                <td class="value">
                    <b>{{ destinationAccount }}</b>
                </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td class="subtitle">Banco:</td>
                <td class="separator"></td>
                <td class="value">
                    <b>{{ destinationBankName }}</b>
                </td>
            </tr>
        </table>
    </div>

    <footer>
        <p class="note">
            Nota: La fecha hora de este mensaje puede variar respecto a la fecha y hora real de la operación
            transaccional. Esto depende de sus servicios de correo electrónico y/o computadora respecto al horario de su
            zona.
        </p>
        <p class="note">Dudas o aclaraciones dirigirse al área correspondiente de la empresa
            <a href="https://cpay.mx" class="color-primary" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">CENTRALPAY</a>.
        </p>
        <img src="https://viabo.com/production_images/cpay/cpay-footer-2x.png" alt="Footer"
             style="width: 100%; max-width: 600px; margin-top: 20px; border-radius: 8px;">
    </footer>
</div>
</body>

</html>
